# <%= appName %> — Domain Driven Design

Tactical DDD patterns with strict dependency direction: **Domain must not depend on database, framework, or external APIs.**

## Structure

```
src/
  domain/
    entities/         # User, Order
    value-objects/    # Email, Money
    aggregates/       # OrderAggregate
    events/           # UserCreated
  application/
    commands/         # CreateUserCommand
    queries/          # GetUserQuery
    services/         # application services
  infrastructure/
    database/
      interfaces/     # IUserRepository
      repositories/   # PrismaUserRepository
  bounded-contexts/   # optional context map
```

